---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Remodel & ADU Plumbing | Berkeley Plumbing — Conejo Valley, CA"
  description="Custom remodel and ADU plumbing by a C-36 licensed contractor in Newbury Park, CA. Kitchen, bathroom, and full ADU plumbing built to California code. CSLB #1115151."
>

  <!-- Page hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy-900 text-white py-16 lg:py-24 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/" class="text-copper text-sm hover:text-copper-light mb-6 inline-block">← Back to home</a>
      <p class="text-copper font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Services</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-5">Remodels and ADU Plumbing</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Kitchen remodels, bathroom additions, whole-home repipes, and complete ADU plumbing systems. Every job designed to pass California inspection on the first walk-through.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

      <!-- Main content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 prose prose-slate max-w-none">

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">Custom Remodel Plumbing</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Remodels require precision: existing systems need to integrate with new work without disrupting what's already functioning. Berkeley Plumbing approaches every remodel with that in mind, mapping the existing layout before recommending any changes and coordinating with tile setters, cabinetmakers, and general contractors to sequence work correctly.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          From a primary bathroom expansion in Westlake Village to a full kitchen gut-and-rebuild in Agoura Hills, I handle the plumbing scope personally, start to finish.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-navy-900 mt-6">Remodel Services</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Kitchen plumbing: sink, dishwasher, and refrigerator line rough-in and finish</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Bathroom remodels: shower, tub, toilet, vanity, and custom fixture setting</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Outdoor kitchen and entertainment area plumbing</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Custom outdoor showers</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Whole-home repipe (copper or PEX)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Laundry room plumbing</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mt-8">ADU Plumbing</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Accessory dwelling units require full, independent plumbing systems: separate supply, drain, and vent lines that meet California code for a livable unit. The complexity is higher than a standard addition, and the inspection requirements are stricter.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Berkeley Plumbing has completed ADU plumbing projects across Newbury Park, Thousand Oaks, and the surrounding Conejo Valley. I work with homeowners and their architects early in the process so the plumbing layout is planned correctly before walls go up.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-navy-900 mt-6">ADU Plumbing Services</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Full rough-in: supply, DWV (drain, waste, vent) systems</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Kitchen and bath finish plumbing</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Water heater installation (tankless preferred for space savings)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Connection to existing main line and utility services</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Permit coordination and inspection support</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-copper/5 border border-copper/20 rounded-lg p-5">
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-navy-900">Planning an ADU?</strong> The best time to involve a plumber is before permits are submitted. Early coordination prevents costly plan revisions and ensures the layout works for both the build and the inspection. Reach out at the design stage.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="bg-stone-warm rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100 sticky top-24">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-4">Request an Estimate</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-5 leading-relaxed">
            Describe your remodel or ADU project and I'll provide upfront pricing before work begins.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="block w-full bg-copper hover:bg-copper-light text-white font-semibold py-3 px-5 rounded text-center transition-colors mb-3"
          >
            Get an Estimate
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:(310) 733-7808"
            class="block w-full border border-slate-300 hover:border-navy-800 text-slate-700 font-semibold py-3 px-5 rounded text-center transition-colors text-sm"
          >
            Call (310) 733-7808
          </a>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> CSLB #1115151</p>
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> ADU specialist</p>
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Code-compliant work</p>
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Upfront pricing</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service areas -->
  <section class="py-12 px-4 bg-stone-warm border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm text-center">
        Remodel and ADU plumbing in:
        <a href="/service-areas/newbury-park/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Newbury Park</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/agoura-hills/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Agoura Hills</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/thousand-oaks/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Thousand Oaks</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/westlake-village/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Westlake Village</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/calabasas/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Calabasas</a>, and surrounding communities.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
